<title>JESUS SAVE</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kipah Aw gi chuh I zau,
 Isu'n a hukdam hi!
 A thu gam tinah gen un,
 Isu'n a hukdam hi!
 Gamtin ah A thu puou in,
 Lamto leh tuilien gal ah!
 Pang un! Lal thupiek ahi,
 Isu'n A hukdam hi!

[V2]
 2. Tui kinawk mahleh gen un,
 Isu'n A hukdam hi!
 Gilote kawmah gen un;
 Isu'n A hukdam hi!
 Tuikuol gamte'n la sau un,
 Tuisuohgiet in gensawn hen;
 Leichung kipak zing ta'n a,
 Isu'n A hukdam hi!

[V3]
 3. Sepgim, dahna ah lasau,
 Isu'n A hukdam hi!
 A thih leh hin tawp loin,
 Isu'n A hukdam hi!
 Lungkham lai inle sau in,
 Lunggil panpih ngaih lai in;
 Than nuoisieh in zawh lasau,
 Isu'n A hukdam hi!

[V4]
 4. Huihnung inle phuongzak hen,
 Isu'n A hukdam hi!
 Nam tin tuhin kipak hen,
 Isu'n A hukdam hi!
 Hukdamna manbei phuongun,
 Tuipi chung leh gamtin ah;
 I guolzawhna lau zie hi,
 Isu'n A hukdam hi!</lyrics>
</song>